ledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FIEPD7RY4IZEITJONT7Z4HQLDN4%2F&h=7b94334a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/IEPD7RY4IZEITJONT7Z4HQLDN4/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"呢倏臭閪會死得好慘"},{"pid":"479b027bd55cf4e78ec39f053e43d002b84c5a19","tid":2261053,"uid":291557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"掃把星幫雜種含L喇，聽佢講一定冇運行"},{"pid":"6bce56fa46f67372f7a8fbb9ac57a2f0cf5a0967","tid":2261053,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d1e2a4a4025ac1e79b759b73035f49157b3cdd3","tid":2261053,"uid":23635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72f817959b4b45f47e7f252ba7f87fe60f5d0a5b","tid":2261053,"uid":194120,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"我見過高海寧，王君馨，呂慧儀.........咁咪全部都係我條女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"可唔可以搵啲好嘅例子？呢幾個已經開始唔惦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"以前做茄喱啡嗰陣見過真人，而家冇做見唔都D新女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb33a5281da9ba566c62c460f446235beb6360a9","tid":2261053,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"我係香港讀書即係都知香港d 衰野啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebc4ab85e6c78e1f5be6321b3dc3d0646f770fc","tid":2261053,"uid":50196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"郭榮鏗仲死攬三權分立<br />\n死都唔肯對外宣稱香港司法系統經已收皮<br />\n呼籲外國法官唔好入染缸<br />\n<br />\n唔通呢一刻政府口講有三權分立<br />\n郭榮鏗會覺得條氣順啲？<br />\n自己去睇呢一年嘅法院判決啦<br />\n仲喺度玩咬文嚼字 濛湖大眾"},{"pid":"0a70b5bdb65f942a36d7690c2b297ceecad9c841","tid":2261053,"uid":284855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:55:53.000